productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Canada and I bought one.
My neighbor Julisa has one of these. She works as a bartender and she says it looks crooked.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Tennessee keeps them away.
This European Unit of Account 9(E.U.A.-9) works outstandingly well. It grudgingly improves my baseball by a lot.
